last_episode_to_air.name: The Spark of Life
last_episode_to_air.overview: Adam Rutherford reveals how scientists are close to repeating what has happened only once in four billion years - the creation of a new life form.

name: The Cell
overview: Dr Adam Rutherford tells the extraordinary story of the scientific quest to discover the secrets of the cell and of life itself. Every living thing is made of cells, microscopic building blocks of almost unimaginable power and complexity.
